Easy Chicken Burrito

Description

A deliciously simple chicken burrito filled with fresh ingredients and wrapped for a satisfying meal!

Ingredients

  • cooked chicken, shredded: 2 cups
  • flour tortillas: 4 large
  • black beans, canned: 1 cup
  • corn, frozen or canned: 1 cup
  • cheddar cheese, shredded: 1 cup
